<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | SpecTacular</title>

    <!-- Stylesheets -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e0f7fa, #ffffff);
            color: #1d3557;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 120px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

            /* Soft Blue Glow Behind Text */
            .hero::before {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                left: 50%;
                width: 400px;
                height: 200px;
                background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3), transparent);
                transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
                border-radius: 50%;
                z-index: 1;
                filter: blur(40px);
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
                color: #0077b6;
                position: relative;
                z-index: 5;
            }

        .sub-heading {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-weight: 300;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            color: #0a2472;
        }

        /* Glassmorphism Floating Box */
        .floating-box {
            position: absolute;
            top: 40%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 500px;
            height: 250px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Floating Soft Circles */
        .circle {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(173, 216, 230, 0.5);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

            .circle.one {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                top: 10%;
                left: 10%;
            }

            .circle.two {
                width: 160px;
                height: 160px;
                top: 60%;
                right: 15%;
                background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
            }

            .circle.three {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
                bottom: 10%;
                left: 40%;
                background: rgba(100, 149, 237, 0.4);
            }

        /* Content Section */
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

            .content:hover {
                transform: scale(1.02);
            }

            .content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                color: #0077b6;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .content p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="circle one"></div>
    <div class="circle two"></div>
    <div class="circle three"></div>

    <div class="floating-box"></div>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1 data-aos="fade-up">Welcome to SpecTacular</h1>
        <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="sub-heading">Where vision meets style and innovation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>At SpecTacular, we redefine eyewear. Our journey started with a mission—to blend style, comfort, and innovation into every frame. Our carefully crafted specs are designed for visionaries like you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>✔️ Premium Quality Materials</p>
        <p>✔️ Trendy & Durable Designs</p>
        <p>✔️ 100% UV Protection</p>
        <p>✔️ Hassle-Free Returns</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
</body>
</html>